01:11:08,860 --> 01:11:13,220
♫  Questions etched deeply into my shattered heart  ♫

572
01:11:13,220 --> 01:11:17,710
♫  Rekindling the flame of my frozen soul  ♫

573
01:11:17,710 --> 01:11:22,240
♫  Facing the dark night that crashes upon me  ♫

574
01:11:22,240 --> 01:11:25,550
♫  When the world keeps, keeps, keeps  ♫

575
01:11:25,550 --> 01:11:29,360
 Was that the only reason? The ledger? 

576
01:11:29,360 --> 01:11:31,760
 Do not appear before me again, 

577
01:11:31,760 --> 01:11:33,590
 Prince Mu Yeong. 

578
01:11:33,590 --> 01:11:36,550
 We exist in a world apart from him, Hong Deok Su. 

579
01:11:36,550 --> 01:11:41,540
 You will be hurt if you remain with someone with whom you ought not to be. 

580
01:11:41,540 --> 01:11:43,780
 Why have you brought this to me? 

581
01:11:43,780 --> 01:11:46,960
 I must eliminate Cheon. 

582
01:11:46,960 --> 01:11:50,960
 I must protect Father and the royal family. 

583
01:11:50,960 --> 01:11:54,280
 We must restore order to the country. 

584
01:11:54,280 --> 01:11:55,740
 Where have you been this time? 

585
01:11:55,740 --> 01:11:57,210
 You cannot go out freely. 

586
01:11:57,210 --> 01:11:58,550
 Is that an order? 

587
01:11:58,550 --> 01:12:00,390
 Do as I say. 

588
01:12:00,390 --> 01:12:02,420
 That is the best course of action. 

589
01:12:02,420 --> 01:12:05,320
 Master Cheon's son, Cheon Jun Hwa? 

590
01:12:05,320 --> 01:12:09,030
 This is the sole way for me to protect Hong Deok Su. 

591
01:12:09,030 --> 01:12:10,430
 Die! 

592
01:12:10,430 --> 01:12:13,910
 I am the new Master Innkeeper, Cheon Jun Hwa. 

593
01:12:13,910 --> 01:12:17,690
 The three individuals who killed my father twelve years ago 

594
01:12:17,690 --> 01:12:21,070
 will ultimately perish while fighting one another. 

595
01:12:21,070 --> 01:12:25,320
 I shall never give up or cease. 

